The world of Scandal! will be shaken by a mysterious new character, Damon Bradbury, to be played by stage and screen star Craig Urbani. Damon is a rich and successful businessperson who oozes charisma, which draws people towards him. He enjoys taking risks in business and life, so viewers will question some of his choices. But Urbani is no stranger to e.tv, having appeared on Ashes To Ashes as Mickey. This renowned performer has appeared in several other local TV series and stage productions. Catch Scandal! every weekday on e.tv at 7.30pm.